## WHAT THIS PROJECT IS

A Google Apps Script + HTML sidebar application embedded in a Google Sheet.
It is a billing team's claims denial workflow management system.
Users log denied/rejected/underpaid claims, work them through a decision-tree
workflow, and track resolution. Built for a medical billing company (ASP)
serving multiple client practices.

**GitHub repo:** `craigaspmdinc-droid/cwe-v2`
**Current version:** V2.5
**Sheet name:** The Google Sheet this lives in (not stored in code)

