## PRIORITY CALCULATION

```javascript
calculatePriority(dos, timelyFilingDays):
  daysLeft = deadline - today
  ≤ 15  → 'Critical (Past Due)'
  ≤ 30  → 'High (Urgent)'
  ≤ 60  → 'Medium'
  else  → 'Low'
```

Medicare/Medicaid: timelyFilingDays = 365
Default: 90 days (overridden by REF-Payers lookup)
Appeal due days: Medicare=120, Medicaid=90, default=60

Priority is recalculated every time `getIssueData()` is called and
updated in the sheet if it changed.

