## SUPERVISOR VIEW PATTERN (added V2.5)

`getDashboardData()` now returns:
- `myQueue`: claims assigned to current user (unchanged, default view)
- `allQueue`: ALL visible open claims with `assignedTo` field (new)
- `teamMembers`: sorted name array (Admin only)

`CWEApp.html` client-side:
- `initViewingBar(teamMembers)` — builds amber dropdown (Admin only)
- `onViewingChange()` — sets `viewingUser`, calls `renderQueueForViewing()`
- `getQueueForViewing()` — filters `allQueue` by `viewingUser` or current user name
- Queue label updates to "[Name]'s Open Claims" when viewing another user

No server round-trip on view change — pure client-side filter.

