## CODING CONVENTIONS

- All server-side files use `.gs` extension in Apps Script, `.js` in repo
- COL constants are zero-based (match `getValues()[0]` array indices)
- `sheet.getRange(row, COL.X + 1)` — add 1 because getRange is 1-based
- HTML templates use `<?= ?>` for escaped output, `<?!= ?>` for raw HTML
- Dark mode CSS variables: `--bg`, `--surface`, `--accent`, `--warn`, `--danger`, `--text`, `--muted`
- Font stack: IBM Plex Sans (body), IBM Plex Mono (labels/codes)
- Animation classes: `fu1`–`fu6` (fadeUp stagger), `slide-in`
- All user-facing strings through `esc()` helper to prevent XSS

